author: samajammin
content:
Hey folks - apologies but I won't be able to make the calls today.

Quick update, we published a JSON RPC API page on ethereum.org, largely gathered from the info on eth.wiki: https://ethereum.org/en/developers/docs/apis/json-rpc/

We view this as a rough v1 & have some ideas on how to improve it but we welcome any input on it! Feel free to ping me here or raise an issue on our Github. Happy to iterate on this quickly, even if this is just a temporary home for these docs.
